quote.summary: Anhui Conch Material Technology Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the research and development, production and sales of cement admixture, concrete admixture together with their respective in-process intermediaries. The Company's main products include the various types of cement admixture and concrete admixture, the in-process intermediary of cement admixture, being alcohol amine, and the in-process intermediaries of concrete admixture, being polyether monomers and polycarboxylic acid mother liquor. The Company's cement and concrete admixtures are used in the production process of cement and concrete, aiming to speed up the production process, save energy consumption, and reduce the amount of raw materials. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
